Sanitize all equipment with @star san{}
Pour @water{1.5%gal} into the #brew pot{} and heat
Pour @Crushed grains{6%oz} into #grain bag{} and tie off loosely
when the water is at an appropriate steeping temperature 150°F - 165°F place the
grain bag into the brew pot.
Steep grains for ~{20%minutes}.
Remove grain bag and without squeezing allow liquid to drain back into brew pot
-- liquid is now wort
Bring the wort to a rolling boil.
Stir in @dried malt extract{20%oz}

